{"tid":210941,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚注定俾港女恰","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T10:24:08.000Z","uid":32438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10348db4d33ed81998c328a333c9358e1f072a20","tid":210941,"uid":32438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"經過過豉油街既巴絲都知道<br />\n果度有幾條垃圾'金融'港女係度搵人填'問卷'<br />\n（聽講呢d問卷係用黎睇條友有無錢 有錢就氹投資 無錢就拉黎做下線）<br />\n講返正題 頭先我又經過果度<br />\n發現有兩個暗瘡毒撚填緊 仲笑笑口咁填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係度我希望各位巴打勇敢d咁拒絕啦 <br />\n唔係有排煩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申一個星期經過5次 <br />\n每次都唔理  有幾次心情唔好仲大聲咁屌過佢老母 又試過問佢可唔可以唔好咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7aa82180c3f0f8fce3cbf4648f1114b1a27f33","tid":210941,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"好日唔行過果度 一見到就知伏<br />\n仲想纏住我 即刻屌鳩佢"},{"pid":"95ff2616d829b0be1f35e51dc7bc7e70198e30bd","tid":210941,"uid":32438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好日唔行過果度 一見到就知伏<br />\n仲想纏住我 即刻屌鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n我又唔係咁衰既<br />\n但有時心情差咪屌佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7078a73c776dfb0de9b33e8cca214824301cbe66","tid":210941,"uid":32438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"成日拎塊板頂我腹肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}